{"tid":2297410,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺呢單獅子山女子墮崖案好有可疑","createTime":"2020-11-23T09:08:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T13:57:59.000Z","uid":261505,"like":5,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"214ba9587da4482bdfa55aef3331dac30b21359d","tid":2297410,"uid":261505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T09:08:07.000Z","msg":"墮崖身亡女子姓梁（56歲），全身多處有創傷。昨晨她約同五男一女友人行山，各人集合後由黃大仙行去獅子山，至中午12時許各人去到翠竹花園對開一處山坡時，梁婦不慎失足墮崖，友人立刻報警。<br />\n由於墮下位置大石嶙峋山勢險要，友人無法到達，消防到場拯救時需手足並用攀爬，十分驚險，當時她已奄奄一息，其間飛行服務隊直升機曾到場搜尋，其後確認她已傷重身亡。由於山勢險要，最後要由飛行服務隊直升機將死者屍體運走。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n班「友人」會唔會係演員扮🤔<br />\n問過旺角靈婆話獅子山呢日好有冤氣<br />\n有無手足幫手諗同查下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e96cc11bd6874e5c77ae3ff86d2538a7e8f6baaf","tid":2297410,"uid":276068,"like":7,"dislike":43,"score":-36,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T09:09:22.000Z","msg":"仲黎？<br />\n彥霖單野仲炒唔夠車？"},{"pid":"4e48b93f9737b43ad22ea4fa2bbd4b369b53ba05","tid":2297410,"uid":261505,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"e96cc11bd6874e5c77ae3ff86d2538a7e8f6baaf","tid":2297410,"uid":276068,"like":7,"dislike":43,"score":-36,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T09:09:22.000Z","msg":"仲黎？<br />\n彥霖單野仲炒唔夠車？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T09:10:29.000Z","msg":"唔係呢 呢單真係幾可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf437c9d8c908af0a50ebd028f626491844d095b","tid":2297410,"uid":261505,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T09:17:37.000Z","msg":"補返：事發係2020年11月21日12時21分<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n20+11=31 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39039c6f2f45be9f975aee41e94155290725c755","tid":2297410,"uid":56550,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T09:25:53.000Z","msg":"拉鳩你條on9"},{"pid":"b6bb599b43a8bed06bdd8f49e1dd8ca3b0aa3bc4","tid":2297410,"uid":56550,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T09:26:48.000Z","msg":"有病唔好學人抗爭啦<br